I have one, she's very young though ... I'd hoped to *eventually* make a jeweler out of her.  But Jewelry is so VERY expensive to learn, this will be happening a *very* long way down the road ... if at all ... but if she can be of service to your need, you have but to ask.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
